      "dialogAsk": "Oh. It's you. Good — someone should see this. This is the one room I never beat. 4,072 attempts. I counted. I count everything. There's a cog back with the supply pile — my hands shake too much this close to the box to carry small parts. Bring it here and I'll give you something I'm tired of building.",
